'''Telltale G-{}-ames'''是一家美国的游戏制作公司，擅长各种剧情类，同名改编游戏等；并常以章节的形式逐章发售游戏。代表作品包括：《[[行尸走肉_(游戏)|行尸走肉]]》、《[[侦探故事|侦探故事]]》、《[[侏罗纪公园_(游戏)|侏罗纪公园]]》和《[[权力的游戏_(2014年游戏)|权力的游戏]]》等。

== 历史 ==
=== 成立之初 ===
Telltale Games由[[LucasArts|LucasArts]]前员工丹·康纳斯（{{lang|en|Dan Connors}}）、凯文·布鲁纳（{{lang|en|Kevin Bruner}}）、特洛伊·莫兰德（{{lang|en|Troy Molander}}）创办，当时他们正在创作1993年游戏《[[妙探闖通關_大腳之謎|妙探闖通關 大腳之謎]]》的续集《[[妙探闖通關：自由警探|妙探闖通關：自由警探]]》，该开发工作最终于2004年3月3日撤销。公司早期的新闻稿公开回应称项目撤销是公司创立的主因<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.telltalegames.com/company/pressreleases/id-8 | title = Telltale Games, A New Game Development Studio, Opens Doors In Northern California | publisher = Telltale Games press release | date = 2004-10-04 | accessdate = 2009-06-17 | archive-date = 2012-12-30 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkV8Dmc?url=http://www.telltalegames.com/company/pressreleases/id-8 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。Telltale Games团队拥有大量集体创造LucasArts{{le|卢卡斯艺电冒险游戏|LucasArts adventure games|著名经典作品}}的经验。

在技术代理人{{le|艾拉·P·罗福肯|Ira P. Rothken}}的协助下，公司于[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[圣拉菲尔_(加利福尼亚州)|圣拉斐尔]]创立。艾拉负责提供创业种子资金、天使投资收购和涉及《{{le|骨头 (漫画)|Bone (comics)|骨头}}》、《[[妙探闖通關|妙探闖通關]]》、{{le|GameTap|GameTap}}、[[育碧|育碧]]等带动初始收入、市场营销和章回体核心游戏技术开发的交易。

2005年2月11日，公司发布首款游戏《{{le|Telltale德州扑克|Telltale Texas Hold'em|德州扑克}}》，一款扑克牌游戏模拟器，目的主要是测试内部游戏引擎Telltale Tool<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-451 | title = Give us your opinion, we'll give you Telltale Texas Hold'em | publisher = the Telltale Blog | date = 2009-05-15 | accessdate = 2009-06-17 | first = Emily | last = Morganti | archive-date = 2012-12-30 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkVfQ70?url=http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-451 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此后的两款游戏改编自[[杰夫·史密斯|杰夫·史密斯]]的《骨头》漫画丛书，但后来计划的章节被废弃。之后，他们为育碧开发了《[[犯罪现场调查：谋杀的三维|犯罪现场调查：谋杀的三维]]》，尽管它由多个独立章节组成，但专门以单独包发售。这种模式也在后来的作品《{{le|犯罪现场调查：证据确凿|CSI: Hard Evidence}}》、《{{le|犯罪现场调查：致命意图|CSI: Deadly Intent}}》和《{{le|犯罪现场调查：致命阴谋|CSI: Fatal Conspiracy}}》中沿用。

确保超级天使人{{le|马修·勒梅尔|Matthew Le Merle}}和天使投资集团成员等来自[[旧金山湾区|旧金山湾区]]的[[天使投资|天使投资]]后，公司开始向卢卡斯艺电购买完成《萨姆与麦克斯：兼职警察》的权利，但被否决，后来向漫画作者[[史蒂夫·普赛尔|史蒂夫·普赛尔]]成功谋取创建新游戏的权利。与公司以往的作品不同，《{{le|妙探闖通關：拯救世界|Sam & Max Save the World}}》（与GameTap联合发布）是紧凑的每月日程表中系列首个发布的章节——这是游戏产业的里程碑。该系列大获成功，Telltale随后乘势制作系列的另外两季。自那时起，他们继续根据每月的流行认可度制作系列作品。Telltale后来创作的多个系列作品属大型喜剧题材，如改编自《[[超级无敌掌门狗|超级无敌掌门狗]]》、《{{le|家有明星|Homestar Runner}}》的游戏。《[[猴岛传说|猴岛传说]]》改编自卢卡斯艺电著名系列，是公司迄今为止最成功的系列之一，其部分原因是其开发者大多有创作卢卡斯艺电冒险游戏的历史。

=== 试点方案 ===
为了补充普通的章回体游戏，公司于2010年初创建试点方案探索单章游戏，寻找其他游戏玩法和叙事手法，并最终可能将其用在章节游戏<ref>{{cite press release | url = http://wii.ign.com/articles/108/1087938p1.html | title = Telltale Games Kicks Off New Game Pilot Program to Foster Innovation | date = 2010-05-10 | accessdate = 2011-02-20 | publisher = Telltale Games | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120305072323/http://wii.ign.com/articles/108/1087938p1.html | archive-date = 2012-03-05 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。方案推行后的首款游戏《{{le|尼尔森·泰瑟斯：谜题侦探|Nelson Tethers: Puzzle Agent}}》与{{le|格雷厄姆·安娜贝勒|Graham Annable}}合作，于2010年6月中旬发布。而以《萨姆与麦克斯》、《家有明星》和[[Valve|Valve]]的《[[军团要塞2|军团要塞2]]》角色为主题的跨界扑克牌游戏《{{le|怪诞扑克夜|Poker Night at the Inventory}}》和网络漫画《{{le|便宜游乐场|Penny Arcade}}》，则于2010年晚些时候发布。公司后来在2011年继续推出《谜题侦探》续集《{{le|谜题侦探2|Puzzle Agent 2}}》。此外在2013年，公司继续推出《扑克之夜》系列作品《{{le|扑克之夜2|Poker Night 2}}》。试点方案也被公司用来开发新的游戏玩法构思，然而把它们采纳到普通的章回体游戏中。《[[行尸走肉_(游戏)|行尸走肉]]》作为试点方案作品启动，被内部称为“僵尸原型”<ref name="rps pilots">{{cite web |url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/05/17/telltale-on-weird-experiments-revisiting-comedy/ |publisher=Rock, Paper, Shotgun |date=2013-05-17 |accessdate=2013-12-12 |title=Telltale on Weird Experiments, Revisiting Comedy |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120014432/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/05/17/telltale-on-weird-experiments-revisiting-comedy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 发展与专营权收购 ===
确立除了创作喜剧专营权作品的目标后，公司后来选择进一步创作戏剧专营权作品。2010年6月，公司宣布获得[[NBC环球|NBC环球]]开发两部章回体系列改变作品《[[回到未来|回到未来]]》和《[[侏罗纪公园|侏罗纪公园]]》的许可<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2010-06-09-future-jurassic-games_N.htm | title = 'Back to Future,' 'Jurassic Park' to become games | work = [[USA_Today|USA Today]] | agency = Associated Press | date = 2011-02-11 | accessdate = 2010-06-09 | first = Derrek J. | last = Lang | archive-date = 2011-06-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110628200955/http://www.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2010-06-09-future-jurassic-games_N.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2011年2月，带许可性质的进一步系列作品公布，包括与[[华纳兄弟互动娱乐|华纳兄弟互动娱乐]]合作开发的改编自漫画丛书《[[行尸_(漫画)|行尸走肉]]》和《{{le|成人童话|Fables (comics)}}》的系列作品<ref name="allthingsdigitial">{{cite web | url = http://emoney.allthingsd.com/20110217/telltale-signs-that-videogames-will-be-downloaded-not-sold-at-retail/?mod=ATD_skybox | title = Telltale Signs That Videogames Will Be Downloaded, Not Sold at Retail | first = Tricia | last = Duryee | date = 2011-02-17 | accessdate = 2011-02-17 | publisher = [[All_Things_Digital|All Things Digital]] | archive-date = 2012-12-30 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkWpZCo?url=http://allthingsd.com/20110217/telltale-signs-that-videogames-will-be-downloaded-not-sold-at-retail/?mod=ATD_skybox | dead-url = no }}</ref>，以及改编自[[雪乐山|雪乐山]]冒险游戏《[[国王密使系列|国王密使]]》的系列作品<ref>{{cite web | url = http://multiplayerblog.mtv.com/2011/02/18/telltale-confirms-kings-quest-reboot-and-fables-game/ | title = Telltale Confirms 'King's Quest' Reboot And 'Fables' Game | first = Matt | last = Clark | date = 2011-02-18 | accessdate = 2011-02-18 | publisher = MTV | archive-date = 2012-12-30 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkYBV7w?url=http://multiplayerblog.mtv.com/2011/02/18/telltale-confirms-kings-quest-reboot-and-fables-game/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。公司于2013年4月3日证实《国王密使》项目取消<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitaltrends.com/gaming/activision-is-planning-something-for-kings-quest-franchise-rights-reportedly-recovered-from-telltale-games/ |title=Activision is planning something for King's Quest After Recovering the Rights From Telltale Games |date=2013-04-03 |accessdate=2013-04-03 |publisher=Digital Trends |archive-date=2013-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130405013739/http://www.digitaltrends.com/gaming/activision-is-planning-something-for-kings-quest-franchise-rights-reportedly-recovered-from-telltale-games/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

到2010年，公司证明获得成功，年收入达1000万美元，比上年多90%<ref name="allthingsdigitial"/>。这部分要归功于被高级营销副总裁史蒂夫·艾利森在2011年称为“迄今最成功的特许经营游戏”的《[[回到未来系列|回到未来]]》[[回到未来：游戏版|系列]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.joystiq.com/2011/02/18/back-to-the-future-is-telltales-most-successful-franchise/ | title = Back to the Future is Telltale's 'most successful' franchise | publisher = Joystiq | date = 2011-02-18 | accessdate = 2011-02-20 | first = David | last = Hinkle | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110629123735/http://www.joystiq.com/2011/02/18/back-to-the-future-is-telltales-most-successful-franchise/ | archive-date = 2011-06-29 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。艾利森指出，对于大部分游戏，他们只需卖出10万份就能达到收支平衡，但最近他们发行的许多作品比这个数字要多两倍或以上。艾莉森估计《行尸走肉》系列的收益可能在2000万到3000万美元<ref name="allthingsdigitial"/>。公司预计凭借其他专营权作品，工作室及其收入将以类似的速度继续增长。他们宣布计划将工作室员工从90名扩展到140名<ref name="allthingsdigitial"/>。

2011年4月，公司宣布另一部获得许可的章回体系列游戏，该作品改编自后来改编成多部《[[法律与秩序|法律与秩序]]》戏剧的《{{le|法律与秩序：洛杉矶|Law & Order: LA}}》<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/218923/telltales-next-project-law-order-la/ | title = Telltale's next project: Law & Order: LA | first = Pete | last = Davidson | date = 2011-04-18 | accessdate = 2011-04-18 | publisher = GamePro | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/218923/telltales-next-project-law-order-la/&date=2011-11-30+19:02:55 | archivedate = 2011-11-30 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

2012年，公司凭借《行尸走肉》获得迄今最大的成功，游戏在20天内售出100万份<ref name=millionsales>{{cite web |title=Telltale Games' The Walking Dead Sells a Million |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/05/17/telltale-games-the-walking-dead-sells-a-million |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2012-12-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkbaZtj?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/05/17/telltale-games-the-walking-dead-sells-a-million |dead-url=no }}</ref>，荣登[[Xbox_Live|Xbox Live]]<ref>{{cite web |title=The Walking Dead Tops Xbox Live Arcade Chart |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-05-11-the-walking-dead-tops-xbox-live-arcade-chart |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |accessdate=2012-05-15 |archive-date=2012-12-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkcNwD3?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-05-11-the-walking-dead-tops-xbox-live-arcade-chart |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[PlayStation_Network|PlayStation Network]]和[[Steam|Steam]]<ref name=millionsales />销售榜榜首。鉴于游戏首季的成功，公司于2012年7月宣布制作续集<ref name="escapistmagazine">{{cite web |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/118317-TellTale-Games-Planning-The-Walking-Dead-Season-Two |title=Telltale Games Planning The Walking Dead Season Two |publisher=The Escapist |accessdate=2012-07-16 |archive-date=2012-12-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CpdBl7uM?url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/118317-TellTale-Games-Planning-The-Walking-Dead-Season-Two |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="joystiq">{{cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2012/07/07/the-walking-dead-season-2-insinuated-by-telltale/ |title=The Walking Dead Season Two Insinuated by Telltale |publisher=Joystiq |accessdate=2011-03-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CpdCYS9X?url=http://www.joystiq.com/2012/07/07/the-walking-dead-season-2-insinuated-by-telltale/ |archive-date=2012-12-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="gamasutra">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/173786/More_The_Walking_Dead_games_on_the_way_from_Telltale_Activision.php |title=More The Walking Dead Games in the Way From Telltale, Activision |publisher=Gamasutra |accessdate=2011-03-08 |archive-date=2012-12-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CpdDKhJw?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/173786/More_The_Walking_Dead_games_on_the_way_from_Telltale_Activision.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年春，《行尸走肉》售出850万份后，公司总部搬迁，员工从125人扩展至160人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/01/07/the-walking-dead-total-sales/ |title=The Walking Dead sold over 8.5 million copies since release |publisher=PC Gamer |accessdate=2013-01-28 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104071514/http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/01/07/the-walking-dead-total-sales |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

公司后来又宣布了两部系列游戏，一部是改编自[[变速箱软件|变速箱软件]]《[[无主之地|无主之地]]》系列的《{{le|无主之地传说|Tales from the Borderlands}}》，另一部改编自HBO同名电视剧的《[[权力的游戏_(2014年游戏)|权力的游戏]]》，后者是2013年Spike VGX电子游戏奖计划。《无主之地传说》的构思出自2012年Spike电子游戏奖期间公司与变速箱软件间的同桌讨论，当时变速箱提到了《无主之地》系列中的剧情和独一无二的角色。事后，公司与变速箱讨论游戏概念，变速箱倾向于欢迎该项目。《权力的游戏》游戏则在关于其他能做游戏的流行特许经营权作品的公司内部讨论中诞生，大部分人支持《权力的游戏》，认为它在感情上与《行尸走肉》游戏相当。他们与HBO讨论概念，经过一年的谈判获得许可<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.polygon.com/2013/12/23/5224694/how-telltale-teamed-up-with-game-of-thrones-and-borderlands | title = How Telltale teamed up with 'Game of Thrones' and Borderlands | first = Alexa Ray | last = Charles | date = 2013-12-23 | accessdate = 2013-12-23 | publisher = Polygon | archive-date = 2021-02-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210226154051/https://www.polygon.com/2013/12/23/5224694/how-telltale-teamed-up-with-game-of-thrones-and-borderlands | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2014年12月，公司与[[Mojang|Mojang]]公布独立于《[[當個創世神|當個創世神]]》的章回体作品，将于2015年分章发布的《[[我的世界：故事模式|當個創世神故事模式]]》。该作品由公司开发，但将采用《當個創世神》社群输入，以便塑造剧情，这样不会为原版修复任何内容<ref name="minecraftsm">{{Cite web | url = http://www.theverge.com/2014/12/18/7415167/minecraft-story-mode-telltale-games | title = Minecraft is getting a story-driven game from the studio behind The Walking Dead | first = Andrew | last = Webster | date = 2014-12-18 | accessdate = 2014-12-18 | publisher = The Verge | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308201918/https://www.theverge.com/2014/12/18/7415167/minecraft-story-mode-telltale-games | dead-url = no }}</ref>。作品受到公司开发者中的《當個創世神》玩家的启发，还有来自于发布围绕游戏开发的叙事性内容的意识。与公司讨论前夕，Mojang被[[微软|微软]]收购，尽管公司与微软现有的合作关系让开发工作在没有后顾之忧的条件下继续<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-02-10-telltales-new-chapter | title = Telltale's new chapter: Minecraft and a top secret original IP | first = Rachel | last = Weber | date = 2015-02-10 | accessdate = 2015-02-10 | publisher = GamesIndustry.biz | archive-date = 2021-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126214412/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-02-10-telltales-new-chapter | dead-url = no }}</ref>。{{le|巴顿·奥斯瓦尔特|Patton Oswalt}}将为游戏配音<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-07-04-telltale-reveals-minecraft-story-mode-starring-patton-oswalt | title = Telltale's Minecraft: Story Mode unveiled, stars Patton Oswalt | first = Jeffrey | last = Matulef | date = 2015-07-04 | accessdate = 2015-07-05 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-date = 2021-01-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210124101217/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-07-04-telltale-reveals-minecraft-story-mode-starring-patton-oswalt | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2015年2月，[[狮门娱乐|狮门娱乐]]宣布投资公司以制作大量“超级节目”——一个混合电视和电子游戏元素的互动作品，可能通过非传统媒介分销，如[[流媒体|流媒体]]服务。首个“超级节目”计划是公司是一直在开发的一部被认为能够利用这种模式的优势的作品<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2015/02/24/telltale-games-ceo-kevin-bruner-super-show-interview | title = Telltale Games CEO Kevin Bruner discusses new venture The Super Show -- exclusive | first = Jonathan | last = Dornbush | date = 2015-02-24 | accessdate = 2015-02-24 | work = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | archive-date = 2020-12-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201207081227/https://ew.com/article/2015/02/24/telltale-games-ceo-kevin-bruner-super-show-interview/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。除此之外，公司宣布狮门公司首席执行官Jon Feltheimer和{{le|联合技术|Unity Technologies}}CEO约翰·里奇蒂耶洛（{{lang|en|John Riccitiello}}）加入公司董事会<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/02/24/lionsgate-makes-significant-investment-in-telltale-games.aspx | title = Lionsgate Makes ‘Significant Investment’ In Telltale Games | first = Mike | last = Futter | date = 2015-02-24 | accessdate = 2015-02-24 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | archive-date = 2021-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210127001300/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/02/24/lionsgate-makes-significant-investment-in-telltale-games.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>。公司宣布与[[漫威娱乐|漫威娱乐]]于2017年开发至少一部改编自[[漫威漫画|漫威漫画]]的作品<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/04/23/telltale-games-inks-deal-to-produce-marvel-games.aspx | title = Telltale Games Inks Deal To Produce Marvel Games | first = Matt | last = Helgeson | date = 2015-04-23 | accessdate = 2015-04-23 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225195901/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/04/23/telltale-games-inks-deal-to-produce-marvel-games.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2016年6月，公司发行了由The Fun Pimps开发的《[[七日杀|七日杀]]》的[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]版本<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-04-07-telltale-to-publish-open-world-survival-game-7-days-to-die-on-consoles | title = Telltale to publish open-world survival game 7 Days to Die on consoles | first = Jeffrey | last = Matulef | date = 2016-04-07 | accessdate = 2016-04-07 | work = Eurogamer | archive-date = 2016-04-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160409022230/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-04-07-telltale-to-publish-open-world-survival-game-7-days-to-die-on-consoles | dead-url = no }}</ref>。两个月后，公司又发布了由Night School Studio开发的《Mr. Robot:1.51exfiltrati0n》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/8/18/12532664/telltale-mr-robot-exfiltration-ios-android-game-night-school|title=The Mr. Robot mobile game feels like a miniature conspiracy ARG|last=Robertson|first=Adi|date=2016-08-18|work=The Verge|access-date=2016-09-13|publisher=Vox Media|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512211755/https://www.theverge.com/2016/8/18/12532664/telltale-mr-robot-exfiltration-ios-android-game-night-school|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 宣告破产 ===
2018年9月21日，总裁彼得·黑利（{{lang|en|Pete Hawley}}）宣布公司正在“大规模关闭工作室”，大约90%员工（约225到250名）遭遇裁员<ref name="verge closure" /><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2018/09/24/business/telltale-video-games-layoffs.html | title = Telltale, Acclaimed Maker of Story-Based Video Games, Lays Off Most of Its Staff | first = Justin | last = Bailey | date = 2018-09-24 | accessdate = 2018-09-24 | website = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | archive-date = 2018-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180924124613/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/09/24/business/telltale-video-games-layoffs.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。不过，约25人的核心团队会维持运作，“履行公司对董事会及合作伙伴的义务”，包括完成[[Netflix|Netflix]]的《當個創世神故事模式》互动媒体计划<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.gameinformer.com/2018/09/21/narrative-adventure-studio-telltale-games-essentially-closes-down | title = Narrative Adventure Studio Telltale Games Essentially Closes Down | author =  | date =  | website = gameinformer.com | accessdate = 2018-09-21 | archive-date = 2021-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126145953/https://www.gameinformer.com/2018/09/21/narrative-adventure-studio-telltale-games-essentially-closes-down | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://variety.com/2018/gaming/news/walking-dead-game-developer-hit-staff-layoffs-1202952915/ | title = ‘The Walking Dead’ Game Developer Hit With 90% Staff Layoffs as 225 Are Let Go | first = Liz | last = Lanier | date = 2018-09-21 | accessdate = 2018-09-24 | website = Variety | archive-date = 2020-11-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201109021417/https://variety.com/2018/gaming/news/walking-dead-game-developer-hit-staff-layoffs-1202952915/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。丹·康纳斯（{{lang|en|Dan Conners}}）表示，公司准备在最后一个投资方撤出时，关闭新一轮融资。高管层已经决定在没有投资的情形下尽快终止所有制作。尽管康纳斯没有指明那一个投资方会撤出，《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》猜测这或许是[[狮门影业|狮门影业]]。据悉，狮门影业在上周还和Telltale的董事会见面，商讨将Telltale的投资资金撤回给核心电影业务<ref name="variety closure lionsgate">{{cite web | url = https://variety.com/2018/gaming/news/telltale-games-the-walking-dead-studio-closure-1202955309/ | title = How Masterful Narrative Game Makers Telltale Suddenly Lost Everything | first = Brian | last = Crecente | date = 2018-09-24 | accessdate = 2018-09-24 | website = Variety | archive-date = 2021-04-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210418120319/https://variety.com/2018/gaming/news/telltale-games-the-walking-dead-studio-closure-1202955309/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。该杂志还报道称，《[[行尸走肉|行尸走肉]]》电视剧的版权方[[AMC电视网|AMC电视网]]和韩国手机游戏发行商[[SmileGate|SmileGate]]都想投资Telltale，但在Telltale宣布关闭前一天，双方都已撤销计划<ref>{{cite web | url = https://variety.com/2018/gaming/news/amc-smilegate-telltale-closure-1202957632/ | title = AMC, Smilegate Backed Out of Funding Talks With Telltale a Day Before Closure | first = Brian | last = Crecente | date = 2018-09-26 | accessdate = 2018-09-26 | website = Variety | archive-date = 2020-11-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201109032109/https://variety.com/2018/gaming/news/amc-smilegate-telltale-closure-1202957632/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。和Telltale联合打造《行尸走肉》游戏的Skybound Interactive主席丹·穆雷（{{lang|en|Dan Murray}}）表示：“我们深谙Telltale正面临着一些挑战，但消息来得太突然，所有人都措手不及”<ref>{{cite web | url = https://variety.com/2018/gaming/news/skybound-telltale-the-walking-dead-2-1202973863/ | title = Telltale’s ‘The Walking Dead’: Kirkman’s Skybound Discusses What’s Next | first = Brian | last = Crecente | date = 2018-10-10 | accessdate = 2018-10-10 | work = Variety | archive-date = 2021-02-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210213111423/https://variety.com/2018/gaming/news/skybound-telltale-the-walking-dead-2-1202973863/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。不愿透露姓名的Telltale职员告诉《[[The_Verge|The Verge]]》，他们知道公司已经深受财务问题困扰数月，和Netflix交易是管理层用来诱惑投机投资者的手段，如今交易的新闻外泄，公司受到进一步打击<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theverge.com/2018/10/4/17934166/telltale-games-studio-closed-layoffs-end-the-walking-dead | title = The Tragic End of Telltale Games | first = Megan | last = Farokhmanesh | date = 2018-10-04 | accessdate = 2018-10-04 | website = The Verge | archive-date = 2021-04-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210409033043/https://www.theverge.com/2018/10/4/17934166/telltale-games-studio-closed-layoffs-end-the-walking-dead | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

遭遇裁撤的员工纷纷表示事先没有受到警告，公司宣布决定还不到半个小时就被赶出办公室<ref name="verge closure">{{cite web | url = https://www.theverge.com/2018/9/21/17888162/telltale-games-layoffs-the-walking-dead | title = The Walking Dead studio Telltale hit with layoffs | first = Megan | last = Farokhmanesh | date = 2018-09-21 | accessdate = 2018-09-24 | website = The Verge | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308163413/https://www.theverge.com/2018/9/21/17888162/telltale-games-layoffs-the-walking-dead | dead-url = no }}</ref>，没有[[遣散费|遣散费]]，医保福利时长不多。9月24日，前职员获准回到办公室收拾个人财物<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-latest-on-the-telltale-games-closure/1100-6461976/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-11-20 |archive-date=2019-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804012557/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-latest-on-the-telltale-games-closure/1100-6461976/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。突然宣布倒闭，加上员工被裁后缺乏保障，使得一众游戏开发商重新讨论结成工会的必要性。游戏公会（{{lang|en|Game Workers Unite}}）草根运动表示，Telltale雇员的待遇“剥削性”<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2018-09-24-telltales-treatment-of-laid-off-staff-a-problem-endemic-in-the-industry | title = Telltale's treatment of staff "a problem endemic in the industry" | first = Matthew | last = Handradan | date = 2018-09-24 | accessdate = 2018-09-24 | website = GamesIndustry.biz | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308103512/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2018-09-24-telltales-treatment-of-laid-off-staff-a-problem-endemic-in-the-industry | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2018年9月24日，前雇员维尔涅·罗伯茨（{{lang|en|Vernie Roberts}}）代表Telltale的275名全体员工对公司发起[[集体诉讼|集体诉讼]]，指控Telltale违反《{{le|1988年劳工调整及再培训通知法案|Worker Adjustment and Retraining Notification Act of 1988}}》。而加利福尼亚州的要求更加严苛，要求大规模裁员行动至少提前60天通知<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.polygon.com/2018/9/25/17901106/telltale-layoffs-lawsuit-warn-act | title = Telltale hit with class-action lawsuit for breaking labor laws | first = Samit | last = Sarkar | date = 2018-09-25 | accessdate = 2018-09-25 | website = Polygon | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308231413/https://www.polygon.com/2018/9/25/17901106/telltale-layoffs-lawsuit-warn-act | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

Telltale尚未正式回应《我们身边的狼：第二季》、《权力的游戏：第二季》和未定名《怪奇物语》项目等正在开发中游戏的状态，不过下岗员工声称开发这些游戏的团队已经解散<ref name="verge closure" /><ref name="WalkingDeadCanceled">{{cite web | url = https://www.usgamer.net/articles/report-telltale-games-shutting-down-the-wolf-among-us-2-and-stranger-things-canceled | title = Sources: Telltale Games Shutting Down, The Wolf Among Us 2 and Stranger Things Canceled [Update, Correction] | author =  | date =  | website = USgamer.net | accessdate = 2018-09-21 | archive-date = 2018-09-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180921234834/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/report-telltale-games-shutting-down-the-wolf-among-us-2-and-stranger-things-canceled | dead-url = no }}</ref>。9月24日，Netflix宣布“正在评估《怪奇物语》互动媒体化的其他选项”，同时宣布《我的世界：故事模式》计划如期进行<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.polygon.com/2018/9/24/17896054/netflix-stranger-things-telltale-game-update | title = Netflix to still produce Stranger Things game despite Telltale collapse | website = Polygon | accessdate = 2018-10-01 | archive-date = 2018-09-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180930143734/https://www.polygon.com/2018/9/24/17896054/netflix-stranger-things-telltale-game-update | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/what-happened-with-telltale-games-heres-a-timeline/1100-6462046/ | title = What Happened With Telltale Games? Here's A Timeline Of Important Events | website = Gamespot | accessdate = 2018-10-01 | archive-date = 2018-10-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181001182340/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/what-happened-with-telltale-games-heres-a-timeline/1100-6462046/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

9月25日，Telltale如期发布《{{le|行尸走肉：最终季|The Walking Dead: The Final Season}}》第二章，同时表示“多位潜在合作伙伴”联系他们，想协助完成剩下两个章节<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/final-season-of-telltales-the-walking-dead-might-c/1100-6462007/ | title = Final Season Of Telltale's The Walking Dead Might Continue, But Many Questions Remain | first = Eddie | last = Makuch | date = 2018-09-24 | accessdate = 2018-09-24 | website = GameSpot | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309004204/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/final-season-of-telltales-the-walking-dead-might-c/1100-6462007/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。然而，部分玩家对这一决定并不满意，其中{{le|克罗伊·巴尔罗|Cory Barlog}}建议Telltale应该资助被裁撤的开发者完成游戏<ref>{{cite web | url = https://kotaku.com/people-are-conflicted-about-the-future-of-telltales-wal-1829309959 | title = Fans And Developers Are Torn About Whether The Walking Dead Games Should Continue | first = Ethan | last = Gach | date = 2018-09-25 | accessdate = 2018-09-25 | website = Kotaku | archive-date = 2021-03-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210301200809/https://kotaku.com/people-are-conflicted-about-the-future-of-telltales-wal-1829309959 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。两位匿名消息人士向《[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]》的伊森·古彻（{{lang|en|Ethan Gach}}）澄清，公司想说服潜在开发合作伙伴雇佣Telltale裁撤的员工，好让他们远程完成游戏剩下两章<ref>{{cite web | url = https://kotaku.com/telltale-is-looking-for-another-company-to-hire-its-sta-1829503254 | title = Telltale Is Looking For Another Company To Hire Its Staff To Finish ''The Walking Dead'', Sources Say | first = Ethan | last = Gach | date = 2018-10-03 | website = Kotaku | access-date = 2018-11-20 | archive-date = 2021-02-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210228035923/https://kotaku.com/telltale-is-looking-for-another-company-to-hire-its-sta-1829503254 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在2018[[纽约漫展|纽约漫展]]上，《行尸走肉》漫画作者[[羅伯特·柯克曼|羅伯特·柯克曼]]表示他的制作公司{{le|Skybound Entertainment|Skybound Entertainment}}已经和Telltale达成共识，由他们的子公司Skybound Games和Telltale开发团队原班人马完成游戏最后两章<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.polygon.com/2018/10/6/17946806/the-walking-dead-the-final-season-release-complete-finished-telltale-games-skybound-entertainment | title = Deal reached to finish The Walking Dead: The Final Season, company says | first = Owen S. | last = Good | date = 2018-10-06 | website = Polygon | accessdate = 2018-10-07 | archive-date = 2018-10-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181007063434/https://www.polygon.com/2018/10/6/17946806/the-walking-dead-the-final-season-release-complete-finished-telltale-games-skybound-entertainment | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2018年10月4日，剧情设计蕾切尔·诺埃尔（{{lang|en|Rachel Noel}}）表示，她团队中核心成员也被裁撤，公司剩下的人“不多”<ref>{{Cite news | url = https://www.engadget.com/2018/10/04/telltale-lays-off-rest-of-staff/ | title = Telltale reportedly lays off more of its staff (updated) | last =  | first =  | date = 2018-10-04 | website = Engadget | accessdate = 2018-10-05 | archive-date = 2019-05-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190529030154/https://www.engadget.com/2018/10/04/telltale-lays-off-rest-of-staff/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/327978/Report_Telltale_Games_lays_off_remaining_skeleton_crew.php | title = Report: Telltale Games lays off remaining 'skeleton crew' | last = Francis | first = Bryant | date = 2018-10-04 | website = Gamasutra | accessdate = 2018-10-04 | archive-date = 2021-01-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210117195117/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/327978/Report_Telltale_Games_lays_off_remaining_skeleton_crew.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2018年11月14日，Telltale正式申请破产，同时从各大平台上下架所有产品<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/telltale-games-is-closing-bankruptcy-proceedings-b/1100-6463272/ | title = Telltale Games Is Closing, Bankruptcy Proceedings Beginning | first =Eddie | last = Makuch | date = 2018-11-14 | accessdate = 2018-11-15 | work = GameSpot }}</ref>。

=== 重新营业 ===
{{main|诉说游戏 (2018年)}}
2019年8月， LCG娱乐宣布已经收购了Telltale Game的标识等产权，新的游戏工作室将在美国加州的[[马里布_(加利福尼亚州)|马里布]]重新营业，并将在[[科特马德拉_(加利福尼亚州)|科特马德拉]]开设一家卫星工作室。由于此前开发的《行尸走肉》等作品的版权被收回，新工作室可能需要转向开发新的作品<ref>{{cite web | url =https://www.gcores.com/articles/114320 TellTale复活！LCG Entertainment | title =进行了收购并重新展开运作 | work =机核网 | date =2019-08-29 | accessdate =2019-08-29 | archive-date =2019-08-29 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190829060458/https://www.gcores.com/articles/114320 | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url =https://www.polygon.com/2019/8/28/20835854/telltale-games-return-walking-dead-lcg-entertainment | title =Telltale Games is being revived | work =Polygon | date =2019-08-28 | accessdate =2019-08-29 | archive-date =2019-08-28 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190828130417/https://www.polygon.com/2019/8/28/20835854/telltale-games-return-walking-dead-lcg-entertainment | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

== 开发模式 ==
公司自称专注于章节游戏的开发商。许多评论家认为公司是唯一一家做好章节游戏的公司。公司还得到众多电影公司等制作商的赏识，受邀开发搭配游戏的电影，摆脱“看电影和玩游戏不可兼得”的固有模式<ref name="episodic">{{cite web|url=http://uk.gamespot.com/pc/adventure/samandmaxseason1/news.html?sid=6189014&om_act=convert&om_clk=newsfeatures&tag=newsfeatures;title;2|title=Q&A: Telltale tells why ''Sam & Max'' works|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|first=Brendan|last=Sinclair|date=2008-04-10|accessdate=2008-12-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6DIke6mRr?url=http://uk.gamespot.com/news/qanda-telltale-tells-why-sam-and-max-works-6189014|archivedate=2012-12-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3163746|title=Why is Episodic Gaming So Hard?|publisher=1UP.com|first=Philip|last=Kollar|date=2007-10-17|accessdate=2009-04-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkfQfV5?url=http://www.1up.com/news/episodic-gaming-challenges|archivedate=2012-12-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/more-companies-will-move-into-episodic-games-telltale|title=More companies will move into episodic games – Telltale|publisher=GamesIndustry.biz|first=Phil|last=Elliott|date=2009-03-16|accessdate=2009-04-19|archive-date=2012-12-30|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkgTXVo?url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/more-companies-will-move-into-episodic-games-telltale|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://uk.pc.ign.com/articles/962/962852p1.html | title=Are Episodic Games the Future? | publisher=IGN | first=Ryan | last=Geddes | date=2009-03-16 | accessdate=2009-04-19 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkhRlCW?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/03/16/are-episodic-games-the-future | archive-date=2012-12-30 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。公司指出与电影公司和编剧合作能创造出致敬原版电影和特许权作品的强大体验<ref name="allthingsdigitial"/>。

尽管主营开发，公司还重视其自行发布游戏的能力<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shacknews.com/featuredarticle.x?id=266|title=Telltale CEO Dan Connors on Sam & Max|publisher=Shacknews|first=Chris|last=Remo|date=2007-03-19|accessdate=2009-06-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkiXam9?url=http://www.shacknews.com/article/46193/telltale-ceo-dan-connors-on|archivedate=2012-12-30}}</ref>，唯一能与其经典的开发商-发布商关系的作品是[[育碧|育碧]]的《犯罪现场调查》游戏。公司已与{{le|GameTap|GameTap}}达成《萨姆与麦克斯》重制版前两季的财政安排，但其余的发行安排在游戏完工并透过数字渠道发售后作出<ref name="dan-gamasutra1">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=23178|title=Interview: Telltale's Connors On Episodic Gaming's Bite|publisher=Gamasutra|first=Chris|last=Remo|date=2009-05-06|accessdate=2009-06-13|archive-date=2012-12-30|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkjPF47?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=23178|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

公司的目标是尽可能地在众多平台和数字发行渠道中出现<ref name="dan-joystiq">{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2009/02/10/joystiq-interview-telltales-dan-connors-on-xbla-wallace-and-gro/|title=Joystiq interview: Telltale's Dan Connors on XBLA, Wallace & Gromit|publisher=Joystiq|first=Christopher|last=Grant|date=2009-02-10|accessdate=2009-06-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DIkkOLbs?url=http://www.joystiq.com/2009/02/10/joystiq-interview-telltales-dan-connors-on-xbla-wallace-and-gro/|archive-date=2012-12-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。迄今为止，他们已透过GameTap、除了自营网络商店外的[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]和[[OS_X|OS X]]版的[[Steam|Steam]]及类似的服务、[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台的[[Xbox_Live_Arcade|Xbox Live Arcade]]和光碟、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]的[[PlayStation_Network|PlayStation Network]]和光碟，[[iPhone|iPhone]]和[[iPad|iPad]]的[[iTunes|iTunes]]、[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]和[[Kindle_Fire_HDX|Kindle Fire HDX]]发布作品<ref name="mixnmojo.com">{{cite web |url=http://mixnmojo.com/news/The-Walking-Dead-Season-One-is-Out-For-Kindle-Fire-HDX |title=The Walking Dead is Out For Kindle Fire HDX |publisher=The International House of Mojo |date=2013-01-06 |accessdate=2013-01-07 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225051442/https://mixnmojo.com/news/The-Walking-Dead-Season-One-is-Out-For-Kindle-Fire-HDX |dead-url=no }}</ref>。尽管公司经常把他们自己的游戏接入其他系统，但《[[犯罪现场调查：谋杀的三维|犯罪现场调查：谋杀的三维]]》却被[[育碧|育碧保加利亚工作室]]移植到[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/csi-3-dimensions-of-murder-review/1900-6181207/ |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |title=CSI: 3 Dimensions of Murder Review |accessdate=2014-01-03 |archive-date=2020-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407101348/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/csi-3-dimensions-of-murder-review/1900-6181207/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，《{{le|骨头：走出骨头乡|Bone: Out from Boneville}}》被Vanbrio移植到Mac OS<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20061013005193/en/Vanbrio-Releases-Jeff-Smiths-Bone-Boneville-Macintosh#.UsgeCvuzFNE |publisher=Business Wire |date=2006-10-13 |title=Vanbrio Releases Jeff Smith’s Bone: Out from Boneville Now Available for the Macintosh |accessdate=2014-01-04 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226005738/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20061013005193/en/Vanbrio-Releases-Jeff-Smiths-Bone-Boneville-Macintosh#.UsgeCvuzFNE |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年的PlayStation会议上，公司被索尼证实是[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]第三方支持提供商之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mixnmojo.com/news/Two-Tantalizing-Tidbits |title=Two Tantalizing Tidbits |publisher=The International House of Mojo |accessdate=2013-02-24 |date=2013-02-24 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225054010/https://mixnmojo.com/news/Two-Tantalizing-Tidbits |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年1月，丹·康纳斯卸任首席执行官，联合创办人凯文·布鲁纳接替其职位。康纳斯指出伴随着公司的持续发展，他们开始经历一些成长中的痛苦，布鲁纳接任首席执行官能更好地引领公司为未来更大的扩展寻找进一步的机会。康纳斯保留公司董事会职位，并担任创意顾问<ref name="bruner ceo"/>。布鲁纳表示，作为变化的一部分，除了继续创作获许游戏，公司目前正在开发基于自主[[知识产权|知识产权]]的作品<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/telltale-games-has-an-original-ip-in-the-works/ | title = Telltale Games has an 'original IP' in the works | first = Shaun | last = Prescott | date = 2015-01-12 | accessdate = 2015-01-12 | work = PC Gamer | archive-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210119001104/https://www.pcgamer.com/telltale-games-has-an-original-ip-in-the-works/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

公司的游戏据报面临着漏洞和不寻常程度的技术缺陷，这可能会阻碍玩家在游戏中取得进展。[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]2015年的一篇文章指出，“他们的游戏可能在许多方面来说很精彩，但也伴随着玩家对广泛的漏洞和故障感到愤怒的暗流”，并总结称公司的技术支持论坛“描绘出发行商不断发行越野车级甚至是直接破碎的游戏的众生相”，而不用资源来修复甚至解决大部分的问题<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hamilton|first1=Kirk|title=A Chronicle Of Buggy, Broken Telltale Games, 2012-2015|url=http://kotaku.com/a-chronicle-of-messed-up-telltale-games-2012-2015-1685685025|accessdate=2015-02-16|work=Kotaku|date=2015-02-16|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015718/https://kotaku.com/a-chronicle-of-messed-up-telltale-games-2012-2015-1685685025|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

